{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fdd7a4783d","title":"致华中局等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ec07bb25ca","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":5,"articleId":"fdd7a4783d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"48e6ce4f6a","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fdd7a4783d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致华中局并告湖南省委电的主要内容。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b4e67c186b","type":"title","text":"致华中局等电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fdd7a4783d"},{"id":"48e6ce4f6a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）我军接管长沙后，除成立长沙军事管制委员会（李明应参加为委员）外，湖南省政府及湖南军区两机构不要马上成立，即用长沙军管会名义统一指挥已占各县。（二）我军入长沙，望注意维持良好秩序，极力注意做程潜、陈明仁及其一派人物中的工作，尊重他们，给他们以起义者的待遇，帮助他们进步，团结多数，打击反动分子。以便经过这种统一战线的方式，顺利地接管全省政权及改编陈明仁军队为人民解放军","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fdd7a4783d"}],"page":{"id":"8786774740","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"fdd7a4783d","start":113,"end":113}}}},"__N_SSG":true}